# Live at the Kings Head Inn

'[https://www.allmusic.com/album/live-at-the-kings-head-inn-mw0001105370 Live at the King's Head Inn]' is Avail's first live album, released on [https://www.discogs.com/label/40551-Old-Glory-Records Old Glory Records] in 1994 on 10" Vinyl and reissued by Jade Tree Records in 2006 as bonus tracks to the Dixie album reissue.
